{"tid":2113221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中國擔任人權理事會「言論自由專員」甄選委員會主席。人權理事會是下一個WHO。","createTime":"2020-07-18T03:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T05:09:43.000Z","uid":48040,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e201513d42e717a65a1ebaf415be0786673342","tid":2113221,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:28:17.000Z","msg":"中國擔任人權理事會「言論自由專員」甄選委員會主席，然後選出了Irene Khan擔任新一任「言論/表達自由專員」。<br />\nIrene Khan是否可以捍衛言論自由就唔知啦（她10年前擔任國際特赦組織主席，最後不歡而散），但佢對中國十分友好就非常明顯。類似譚德塞。<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">所以，人權理事會可能變成下一個WHO。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你可能會問，咁美國點解唔出聲？<br />\n其實，美國已經係2018年推出人權理事會，原因係：<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">好多極權國家都加入人權理事會，嘗試為自己侵犯人權的紀錄洗白！</span><br />\n呢D極權國家加入人權理事會之後，非常齊心地係理事會中譴責美國的人權狀況。<br />\n所以，「人權理事會」已經變成「極權國家俱樂部」。<br />\n美國覺得自己留係人權理事會，係影衰自己。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1284161678540550144?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1284161678540550144%3Fs%3D20&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=8895d2d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSomethinkMore%2Fstatus%2F1284161678540550144%3Fs%3D20&h=1f96df52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SomethinkMore/status/1284161678540550144?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"553e3d356c9304d87e644c2957462afa53bbf8d4","tid":2113221,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:30:37.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"2c900771fd68a5cdd06269e694f63a7ea6294ff2","tid":2113221,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"917a4b81d3712f9688fb536b7a3f1e5c944814f6","tid":2113221,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T03:37:02.000Z","msg":"wabdsiu"},{"pid":"7775cc61952a2b132e7ca757d83ee9b240e62e2f","tid":2113221,"uid":34409,"like":2,"disl